Responsibilities:
· To conduct classroom teaching and student care duties
· To teach Primary &amp; Secondary English, Mathematics, Science
· To provide guidance in Primary Chinese
· Be in-charged of Administrative Duties

Requirements:
· Able to work on Saturday
· Bilingual in English and Mandarin
· Minimum ‘A’ levels, Diploma holders &amp; above
· Committed, responsible &amp; energetic
· On the job training provided, fresh school leavers welcomed to apply.